            "subtype": "ability",
            "success": "The creature is sickened 1. ",
            "text": "The viper vine releases a 60-foot emanation of invisible pollen that stays in the air for 5 rounds unless dispersed by a moderate or stronger wind. Each creature that enters or starts its turn in the area must succeed at a DC 33 Will save or be captivated. The viper vine can't use Captivating Pollen for 1d4 rounds. ",
